NameFlagsCard.TypeDescription & Constraints
AnimalSurveillance 0..*BackboneElement
Elements defined in Ancestors: @id, extension, modifierExtension
Logical Model - Animal Surveillance
Instances of this logical model are not marked to be the target of a Reference
reportingDate 0..1dateReporting Date
epidemiology 0..1BackboneElementEpidemiology Information
animalClass 1..1codeAnimal Class
Binding: Animal Class Value Set (required)
animalSpecies 0..1codeAnimal Species
Binding: Animal Species Value Set (required)
animalType 0..1codeAnimal Type
Binding: Animal Type Value Set (required)
animalsAtRisk 0..1positiveIntAnimals at Risk
animalsCases 0..1positiveIntAnimals Cases
animalsDeaths 0..1positiveIntAnimals Deaths
animalsDestroyed 0..1positiveIntAnimals Destroyed
animalsSlaughtered 0..1positiveIntAnimals Slaughtered
vaccination 0..1codeIf the animals are vaccinated. YES | NO | UNKNOWN
Binding: Yes/No/Unknown Value Set (required)
vaccinated 0..1positiveIntNumber of vaccinated animals
productionSystemOne 0..1codeProduction System One
Binding: Production System One Value Set (required)
productionSystemTwo 0..1codeProduction System Two
Binding: Production System Two Value Set (required)
clinicalSignsAndNecropsyLesions 0..1BackboneElementClinical signs and necropsy lesions
clinicalSigns 0..5codeClinical signs. Note: can be more than one
Binding: Clinical Signs Value Set (required)
necropsyLesions 0..5codeNecropsy lesions. Note: can be more than one
Binding: Necropsy Lesions Value Set (required)
surveillanceTypeAndInfectionSource 0..1BackboneElementSurveillance type and infection source. Surveillance and Infection source (select all that apply)
surveillanceType 0..1codeSurveillance Type. PASSIVE | ROUTINE | ACTIVE | PDS | CAHO | GDS | SENTINEL
Binding: Surveillance Type Value Set (required)
infectionSource 0..5codeInfection Source.
Binding: Infection Source Value Set (required)
diagnosis 0..1BackboneElementDiagnosis Information
diseaseStatus 0..1codeDisease Status. CONFIRMED | DENIED | SUSPECTED
Binding: Disease Status Value Set (required)
disease 0..1codeDisease
Binding: Diseases Value Set (required)
diseaseSubTypes 0..*codeDisease Subtype(s)
Binding: Disease Subtype Value Set (required)
clade 0..1codeClade
Binding: Clade Value Set (required)
diagnosticSource 0..1codeDiagnostic Source
Binding: Diagnostic Source Value Set (required)
diagnosisBasis 0..1codeDiagnosis Basis. CLINICAL_SIGNS | NECROPSY_LESIONS | LABORATORY_TEST | OTHERS
Binding: Diagnosis Basis Value Set (required)
controlMeasuresAndTreatments 0..1BackboneElementControl measures and treatment (select all that apply)
controlMeasures 0..5codeControl Measure. Note: can be more than one
Binding: Control Measures Value Set (required)
treatments 0..5codeTreatments. Note: can be more than one
Binding: Treatments Value Set (required)
comment 0..1stringAnimal Surveillance Comments

Documentation for this format
